<html>
  <head>
    <title>Two-Factor Authentication Status Update</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;
      max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; } .container {
      background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; } .header {
      text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; } .content { margin-bottom: 20px;
      } .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 0.8em; color: #666; } .button {
      display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Two-Factor Authentication Status Update</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello,</p>

        <p>This email confirms that two-factor authentication has been
          {{action}}
          for your Complete Authentication System account.</p>

        <div
          style="text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0; padding: 1.5rem; background-color: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 6px;"
        >
          <p
            style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280;"
          >Account Security Details:</p>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
            <li>Action: {{action}} two-factor authentication</li>
            <li>Time: {{timestamp}}</li>
            <li>Device: {{device}}</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Security Notice:</strong>
          If you didn't make this change, please:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact our support team immediately</li>
          <li>Review your account activity</li>
          <li>Change your password if you suspect unauthorized access</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Best regards,<br />The Complete Authentication Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to {{email}}.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>